message: ProRata polls give their results rounded to the nearest .0 or .5 figure, so we maintain such criterion and show the extrapolations rounded to the nearest .0 or .5 figure. Basically, because you cannot conduct an exact extrapolation based out of an inexact figure (i.e. The 33% ProRata gives to ND, excluding undecided and abstentionists, means the actual figure is between 32.75% and 33.25%)
